name: Jakes Cheese Land
description:
Welcome to your new job at Jakes Cheese Land! Your a night guard and need to survive Jake and his friends for 5 days. Or 6 if your feeling like you need to stay another night. The animatronic cast includes: Jane, Jordan, Daz, And the one and only JAKE! Also go play the ORIGINAL FNaF.  (I also fixed most bugs before I released it)

FNaF is made by Scott Cawthon.
